dct_description_sm: Hachure relief with depths shown by soundings and spot-shading.
2 profile views, lights and lights vessels tables, buoy legend, storm warning displays, tidal information, abbreviations table, life savings stations, bridge heights, dates of various corrections.
Shows detailed topography (farmland, woods, marshland, etc.), railroads, city plans, streets.
